sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Owner as Site Owner
    participant Sanity as Sanity CMS
    participant Dev as Developer/CLI
    participant GitHub as GitHub Repo
    participant CF as Cloudflare Pages
    participant CDN as Cloudflare CDN
    participant Visitor as Site Visitor

    Note over Owner,Visitor: Content Update and Deploy Workflow

    Owner->>Sanity: Make content changes
    Owner->>Sanity: Click Publish
    Sanity->>Sanity: Save to Content Lake

    Note over Owner,Visitor: Changes saved but NOT live yet

    alt Option A: Manual Upload (Current Method)
        Owner->>Dev: Request deploy
        Dev->>Dev: cd web && npm run build
        Dev->>Dev: Create deploy_package with dist + functions
        Owner->>CF: Login to dash.cloudflare.com
        Owner->>CF: Pages > your-project > Create deployment
        Owner->>CF: Upload deploy_package contents
        Owner->>CF: Click Save and deploy
    else Option B: Retry Previous Build
        Owner->>CF: Login to dash.cloudflare.com
        Owner->>CF: Pages > your-project
        Owner->>CF: Deployments > Retry deployment
        Note right of CF: Uses cached build artifacts
    else Option C: CLI Deploy (Alternative)
        Dev->>Dev: cd web && npm run build
        Dev->>CF: npx wrangler pages deploy dist
        Note right of CF: Requires wrangler CLI setup
    end

    Note over Owner,Visitor: GitHub auto-deploy NOT configured<br/>(manual upload required)

    CF->>Sanity: Fetch content (build time)
    CF->>CF: npm run build (Astro SSG)
    CF->>CF: Generate static HTML/CSS/JS
    CF->>CDN: Deploy to edge locations

    CDN-->>Visitor: Serve updated content

    Note over Owner,Visitor: Changes now live worldwide
